00:25:47.074 --> 00:25:48.074
Because people would come up to you and they’d
be like,

00:25:48.074 --> 00:25:49.074
[Inaudible]

00:25:49.074 --> 00:25:50.074
&gt;&gt; Male #3: And what does that translate to?

00:25:50.074 --> 00:25:51.074
&gt;&gt; Male #2: That means this little black guy.

00:25:51.074 --> 00:25:52.074
[Laughter]
[Music plays]

00:25:52.074 --> 00:25:53.074
Male #4: I grew up in East Chinatown in Toronto.

00:25:53.074 --> 00:25:54.074
So it was made very clear that I was gweilo
from a very early--

00:25:54.074 --> 00:25:55.074
Male #3: Gweilo?

00:25:55.074 --> 00:25:56.074
Meaning?

00:25:56.074 --> 00:25:57.074
Male #4: White ghost.

00:25:57.074 --> 00:25:58.074
So I know every derogatory term for a white
