00:25:58.074 --> 00:25:59.074
[Music plays]

00:25:59.074 --> 00:26:00.074
&gt;&gt; Baratunde Thurston: So that’s some of,
you know what people have to say in the book.

00:26:00.074 --> 00:26:01.074
