00:30:37.589 --> 00:30:40.279
This is my favorite comment by far though.

00:30:40.279 --> 00:30:41.460
[Laughter]
&gt;&gt; Baratunde Thurston: “My girlfriend is

00:30:41.460 --> 00:30:46.510
