scenes, is set up a virtual street team.

00:31:56.009 --> 00:32:00.539
And I had taken some cues from Seth Godin
around this and wanted to tweak it for our

00:32:00.539 --> 00:32:01.539
own campaign.

00:32:01.539 --> 00:32:06.209
So we recruited people, we got over 100 people
folks to sign up to help spread the message

00:32:06.209 --> 00:32:07.679
of the book in their own way.

00:32:07.679 --> 00:32:08.679
So they got the book early.

00:32:08.679 --> 00:32:12.049
I wanted them to blog about it, and they were
not all black.

00:32:12.049 --> 00:32:18.089
This was an international crew, men and women,
um, Asian and Latin American, all kinds of

00:32:18.089 --> 00:32:20.440
folks able to find a connection with some
of these stories.

00:32:20.440 --> 00:32:26.049
Cause the story, black is sort of the variable,
how to be is sort of the heart of the story.

00:32:26.049 --> 00:32:29.399
I contacted everybody I knew.

00:32:29.399 --> 00:32:30.709
[Laughter]
