00:32:43.129 --> 00:32:44.129
you think I should do?”

00:32:44.129 --> 00:32:46.260
He said, “Well did I ask you to buy my book?”

00:32:46.260 --> 00:32:47.260
I was like, “Nope.”

00:32:47.260 --> 00:32:48.260
And he’s like, “That was a miss.”

00:32:48.260 --> 00:32:50.769
He’s like,” You have all these followers
who are actually friends.

00:32:50.769 --> 00:32:52.589
I didn’t hit you up personally.

00:32:52.589 --> 00:32:55.609
The one thing you could do that would be most
