00:32:55.609 --> 00:32:58.489
to talk to people one on one.

00:32:58.489 --> 00:32:59.489
Just do it.

00:32:59.489 --> 00:33:00.489
Do the hard work.”

00:33:00.489 --> 00:33:04.479
And show the shoe leather We got a little
crazy.

00:33:04.479 --> 00:33:06.249
I have a, I’m working with someone.

