00:41:19.640 --> 00:41:20.640
&gt;&gt; Baratunde Thurston: Harvard, cool.

00:41:20.640 --> 00:41:23.040
&gt;&gt; Female #3: And one of the things that I
found was, when I was at Harvard, there was

00:41:23.040 --> 00:41:25.730
a lot of pulling the black card, shall we
